{"id":124100,"type":6,"name":"啞妻","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/de/b6/124100_j5v7n.jpg","summary":"　　琼瑶《六个梦》系列之一。 \r\n　　柳方两家为腹中子女指腹为婚，可惜方家女儿依依一出生便是聋哑儿，为了柳家着想方家即时提出婚约取消，但同样看重情义的柳家毅然拒绝。二十年后，柳静言与方依依父母之命成亲，接受了五四新文化思想熏陶的静言本不满这盲婚哑嫁，然被依依的善解人意才貌双全所吸引，真正彼此相爱。但当依依生下的女儿又是哑巴时，静言无法承受命运的捉弄，于是当依依再次怀孕时他硬生生用计逼她打下一个男婴，依依从此心底充满恨意。懦弱的静言远赴日本，并与一艺妓结婚生子，十年后归来，郁郁而终，留下无言的依依，依旧守候着人生的轨迹…… ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>哑妻</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16898\">瓊瑤</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16659\">劉雪華</a> / 林瑞陽 / 趙永馨 / <a href=\"/person/16714\">金超群</a> / 阮虔芷</li><li><span>集数: </span>19</li><li><span>开始: </span>1990-03-15</li><li><span>结束: </span>1990-04-10</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>台灣</li><li><span>语言: </span>普通话/国语</li><li><span>频道: </span>華視</li><li><span>导演: </span>沈怡</li><li><span>编剧: </span>林齡齡</li>","eps":[{"id":476263,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476263","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476264,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476264","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476265,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476265","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476266,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476266","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476267,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476267","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476268,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476268","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476269,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476269","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476270,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476270","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airda